## 🔄 Essential Workflow Pattern
1. Set context: `spiral context S4.1`
2. Work on code
3. Commit with auto subtask: `spiral commit "description of work" --auto`
4. Check progress: `spiral show S4.1`
5. Repeat until milestone complete
6. Complete milestone: `spiral commit S4.1 --auto`
